<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Contest Invitation - {{contestName}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1a75ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: white;
      background-color: #1a75ff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .contest-info {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #1a75ff;
    }
    .time-info {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1a75ff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Contest Invitation</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>You're invited to participate in the upcoming contest:</p>
    
    <div class="contest-info">
      <h2>{{contestName}}</h2>
      <p class="time-info">Start Time: {{startTime}}</p>
      <p class="time-info">End Time: {{endTime}}</p>
      <p class="time-info">Duration: {{duration}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Don't miss this opportunity to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Test your programming skills</li>
      <li>Compete with other participants</li>
      <li>Improve your rating</li>
      <li>Learn new problem-solving techniques</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Make sure to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Read the contest rules carefully</li>
      <li>Test your coding environment before the contest</li>
      <li>Join a few minutes early to review the problems</li>
    </ul>
    
    <a href="{{contestUrl}}" class="button">Register for Contest</a>
    
    <p>You can set a reminder and review contest details by clicking the button above.</p>
    
    <p>Good luck!</p>
    <p>The Codeforces Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent to {{recipient}}. You received this because you're registered on Codeforces.</p>
    <p>To manage email preferences, visit your <a href="https://codeforces.com/settings">account settings</a>.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Codeforces. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>